        • [ - ] BenForestell - member since 04-Oct-12

          It is kind of sickening looking at who Madrid have coming off the bench. World class players like Ozil, Modric, di Maria, Khedira, Varane (not quite there yet, but has the potential) and Higuain. Best squad depth in all of Europe. Barca may always have three of Alexis, Villa, Tello, Pedro on the bench, as well as Song, Masch and Fabregas sometimes, but consistently, Madrid has the best depth.
